    "instruction": "Load the four CSV files: metric.csv, trace.csv, log.csv, error_logs.csv. For each file, return a compact summary only: 1) total row count, 2) minimum and maximum timestamp, 3) list of unique cmdb_id values (limit to first 50), 4) list of unique KPI/trace/log names (for metric.csv use kpi_name, for trace.csv use trace_name, for log.csv use log_name; for error_logs.csv return the first 50 distinct message snippets or full messages if short), limited to first 50, and 5) the top 5 rows as a sample. Keep outputs text-only and compact."
